flowchart TB
    %% 6-Tier Context Assembly — highest signal to lowest

    T1["Tier 1 — Router<br/>AGENTS.md + MASTER_INDEX.md"]:::t1
    T2["Tier 2 — Repo Memory (Always)<br/>core-policies.md"]:::t2
    T3["Tier 3 — Repo Memory (By Intent)<br/>project-knowledge-base.md / learned-heuristics.md / adr-log.md"]:::t3
    T4["Tier 4 — Feature Artifacts<br/>status.md / spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md<br/>progress.md / handoff.md / claim.md<br/>testing-scenarios.md / session-extracts.md"]:::t4
    T5["Tier 5 — Raw Code<br/>JIT read of immediate task-scoped source files"]:::t5
    T6["Tier 6 — Transient Logs<br/>Command outputs, test logs, subagent summaries"]:::t6

    T1 -->|always loaded| T2
    T2 -->|loaded on keyword match| T3
    T3 -->|loaded on active slug| T4
    T4 -->|read JIT as needed| T5
    T5 -->|run commands/proofs| T6

    T6 -.->|compaction: summarize + evict| T4
    T5 -.->|evict JIT files after task| T4

    LOAD["Load Rules:<br/>Tier 1-2 always · Tier 3 by intent keyword match<br/>Tier 4 on active feature slug · Tier 5 JIT · Tier 6 transient/evicted"]:::note

